mu camu are central to its identity.", "Mexican cuisine is a vibrant blend of indigenous Mesoamerican and Spanish influences, known for tacos, enchiladas, and mole sauces. It relies heavily on corn, beans, chili peppers, and fresh herbs like cilantro."], "scores": [0.5962839536648193, 0.5600894001139283, 0.5145032642505803, 0.5043526803998688, 0.4990280722212692], "model_name": "mpnet", "document_ids": ["Ethiopian", "Spanish", "Indian", "Peruvian", "Mexican"]}}